#. module: real_estate_management
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:real_estate_management.report_contract_document
msgid ".\n                        It shall be paid monthly in advance, within the first\n                        seven (7) days of each month, by cash deposit or bank\n                        transfer in favour of the Lessor"
msgstr ".\n Se pagará mensualmente por meses anticipados, dentro de los siete (7) primeros días de cada mes, mediante ingreso en metálico o transferencia bancaria a favor del Arrendador"

#. module: real_estate_management
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:real_estate_management.report_contract_document
msgid ".\n                        Payment shall be sufficiently evidenced by the\n                        corresponding deposit or transfer receipt or, if paid\n                        in cash, by the receipt issued by the Lessor."
msgstr ".\n El pago se acreditará suficientemente mediante el correspondiente resguardo de ingreso o transferencia o, si se paga en metálico, mediante el recibo expedido por el Arrendador."

#. module: real_estate_management
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:real_estate_management.report_contract_document
msgid ".\n                        The Lessor hereby delivers, with the signing of this\n                        contract, the keys to the leased dwelling and its\n                        possession, together with the energy efficiency\n                        certificate. The Lessee receives the dwelling with full\n                        knowledge of its conditions and submits to the\n                        horizontal property regime, undertaking to:"
msgstr ""

